<linker>
  <!--
    IL2CPP / managed code stripping prevention.
    The shared deterministic simulation is consumed via reflection-friendly System.Text.Json
    source generators, but defensive `preserve="all"` is the simplest correct option for now.
    Once we ship JsonSerializerContext sources, we can scope this down per type.
  -->
